name: De Ammon #001 : The Hunter in the middle of the night
description: On the ridge of the misty hill that did not penetrate the sun, he finally arrived at the coordinates he had found through his strange sight and hearing. De Ammon tells the story of the journey of a child descended from a wise demon and an arrogant angel, he explores a world full of surprises. He reads nature and plays unlimited sensory expressions through his spiritual experiences.
